{
  "id": "adv_main_02_12_03",
  "title": "東京編2章33話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……ごめんなさい\n結局私達じゃ、スリクスには勝てなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… I'm sorry.\nIn the end‚ we couldn't beat ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんで琴乃ちゃんが謝るの？\nライブ、今までで一番良かったよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-why is Kotono-chan apologizing?\nIt was the best live performance yet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "でも勝てなかった\nさくら達には、記者への囮までやってもらったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we didn't win.\nAnd you even acted as a decoy for the reporters…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで。おかげであんな素敵なステージを\n観られたって思えば、お安い御用だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it. If it means I got to see such a wonderful stage‚\nit was a small price to pay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.1905628155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう\nそれから、トリエルのみんなにも……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nAnd to everyone in TRINITYAiLE too… I'm sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "謝ることなんてない。お互い、やれることはやった\nそれで届かなかったなら、仕方ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no need to apologize. We all did what we could.\nIf it didn't reach them‚ it can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、さくらの真似じゃないけど\n今までで一番、輝いていたステージだったと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But just like Sakura‚\nI think it was your most radiant stage yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、琴乃達はもっと胸を張っていいはずよ\n……お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you should all hold your heads high‚ Kotono and the others.\n…Good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そうだ。みんなの言う通り\n最高のステージだったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that's right. Just like everyone said‚\nit was the best stage ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 71.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく。星見プロからの出場者は\nいよいよサニピだけになったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ the only participant left\nfrom Hoshimi Pro is Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.6433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "特訓はずっと莉央さん達リズノワが見てくれてたけど\n実際のところ、どうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san and LizNoir have been overseeing their training‚ but\nhow are they doing‚ actually?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "順調よ。確実にみんな、レベルアップしている\nトリエルにも手伝ってもらうことになったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're doing well. They're definitely leveling up.\nWe've also had TRINITYAiLE help out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央ちゃん達が、私達それぞれの長所を伸ばすために\nいろいろメニューを組んでくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-chan and the others have put together various menus\nto help each of us develop our strengths.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "怜はダンス技術の底上げのため、葵が見ているわ\n千紗は、全力で踊りきるための体幹トレーニング……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi is watching over Rei to improve her basic dance skills.\nChisa is doing core training to dance with all her might…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんは、周りをよく見る分、自分のことが\n疎かになりがちだから、その意識改善を徹底的に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san tends to neglect herself because she's always paying attention to those around her‚\nso we're thoroughly working on improving her awareness of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらと雫は、歌唱力の底上げに注力しているわ\nきっと二人の歌が、打倒スリクスの要になる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm focusing on improving Sakura and Shizuku's singing abilities.\nTheir singing will surely be the key to defeating ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "二人の特訓は、私がずっと見ていたんだけど\n瑠依にも手伝ってもらうことになったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been watching their training‚ but\nI've also had Rui help out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、ありがとう\n必要な物や手伝えることがあれば、遠慮なく言ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand‚ thank you.\nIf you need anything or if there's anything I can help with‚ don't hesitate to tell me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら達は、体調とか大丈夫か？\n特訓も重要だが、体調を崩したら元も子もない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are you all doing‚ Sakura and the others?\nTraining is important‚ but it's all for nothing if you get sick.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、はい。体調は全然、大丈夫ですよ\nちゃんと、成長してる！　って実感もありますし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ yes. I'm perfectly fine.\nI can really feel myself growing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（……なんだか、いつものさくららしくないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…She doesn't seem like her usual self.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もし何かあれば無理しないで教えて……ん？\n電話……え！？　三枝さんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anything's wrong‚ don't push yourself and tell me… Huh?\nA call… Huh!? It's from Saegusa-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.333333299993,
          "startTime": 160.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666667000015,
          "startTime": 167.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 168.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……も、もしもし、三枝さん？\n三枝さんですよね！？　もしもし！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…H-hello‚ Saegusa-san?\nIt's Saegusa-san‚ right!? Hello!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だ、ちゃんと聞こえている\n久しぶりだな。元気そうで安心した",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ I can hear you clearly.\nIt's been a while. I'm relieved you're doing well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええ……おかげさまで……って\n三枝さん、今どこにいるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah… Thanks to you… but\nwhere are you now‚ Saegusa-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの、三枝さん！　さくらです！\n今、何してるんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ um‚ Saegusa-san! It's Sakura!\nWhat are you doing now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "というか、無責任過ぎよ！\n今まで事務所や所属アイドルをほったらかして……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is irresponsible!\nNeglecting the office and your idols all this time…!",
