      "text": "莉央もそこにいるのか……実際、その通りだな\nみんなには、申し訳ないことをしたと思っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio is there too… You're right.\nI know I've done a terrible thing to all of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
