      "text": "詫びは必ず入れるし、どう責められても構わない\nでも今は、先に大事な話をしなくちゃいけない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll definitely apologize‚ and you can blame me all you want.\nBut right now‚ I need to tell you something important first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
