      "text": "朝倉を救い出し、姫野の陰謀を阻止する準備が\nようやく整いそうなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparations to rescue Asakura and stop Himeno's scheme\nare finally coming together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
