      "text": "その声は、天動さんだね？\n今までよく耐えてきたな。もうあと少しの辛抱だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that you‚ Tendo-san?\nYou've endured well. Just a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shj.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_12_03-shj006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、具体的なことはまだ話せない。姫野のやり方は\nとにかく周到だ。どこで聞かれているか分からない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't tell you the details yet. Himeno's methods are\nthorough. We don't know who might be listening.",
